    <entry>
      <title>如何为多个Github账号设置SSH keys</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/23/How-to-create-multi-SSH-keys-for-Git/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/23/How-to-create-multi-SSH-keys-for-Git/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天在尝试提交第二个Github账号下的项目内容时提交失败，下面记录一下解决过程。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; git push origin main</span><br><span class="line">kex_exchange_identification: Connection closed by remote host</span><br><span class="line">Connection closed by 192.30.255.112 port 22</span><br><span class="line">fatal: Could not read from remote repository.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Please make sure you have the correct access rights</span><br><span class="line">and the repository exists.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>错误中提到无法从远程仓库中读取内容，需要确认是有正确权限以及远程仓库项目是否建立。</p><p>1.首先确保远程仓库已经建立。</p><p>2.然后通过添加SSH Key给第二个Github账户建立安全连接。多个Git平台是可以共用同一对密钥的，比如Github，Bitbucket，Gitee平台三个平台之间用同一对是没问题的。但是同一平台内不同账户必须用不同的密钥对，比如Github平台的账户A和账户B，必须是不同的密钥。</p><p>之前在为BitBucket已经创建过id_rsa密钥对，用在此前的Bitbucket账号A和Github账号B上都没有问题，现在遇到问题的项目是Github账号C上的，那么需要为他创建新的密钥对。</p><p>注意这里需要命名新的文件名。使用默认文件名可能会覆盖原有文件，那么原有文件的密钥便失效了，用到了这个密钥的平台则都需要更改。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;comment&quot;</span><br><span class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file in which to save the key (/Users/lily/.ssh/id_rsa): /Users/lily/.ssh/id_rsa_accountC</span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):</span><br><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:</span><br><span class="line">Your identification has been saved in /Users/lily/.ssh/id_rsa_accountC</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved in /Users/lily/.ssh/id_rsa_accountC.pub</span><br><span class="line">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class="line">SHA256:RTKN6c9D2BqrmS3EVfo+FjSlCRQD4aJyZpe6IWehUGI comment</span><br><span class="line">The key&#x27;s randomart image is:</span><br><span class="line">+---[RSA 3072]----+</span><br><span class="line">|      o+*=.      |</span><br><span class="line">|     .  +=o .    |</span><br><span class="line">|.E. . .. *.+     |</span><br><span class="line">|.o . o  *.B      |</span><br><span class="line">|o * o. .SX .     |</span><br><span class="line">|.* +  o o *      |</span><br><span class="line">|o =  . = . o     |</span><br><span class="line">| + o  = . +      |</span><br><span class="line">|  .    . . .     |</span><br><span class="line">+----[SHA256]-----+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.接下来需要在.ssh文件夹内添加config文件并加上配置，如果已有config则打开编辑即可。默认情况下GIt会寻找默认文件id_rsa的密钥进行授权匹配，有了config文件，系统会根据其中配置读取指定密钥。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Host accountB.github</span><br><span class="line">    HostName github.com</span><br><span class="line">    user git</span><br><span class="line">    IdentityFile &quot;~/.ssh/id_rsa&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    IdentitiesOnly yes</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Host accountC.github</span><br><span class="line">    HostName github.com</span><br><span class="line">    user git</span><br><span class="line">    IdentityFile &quot;~/.ssh/id_rsa_accountC&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    IdentitiesOnly yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其中Host是自己命名的域名别名，HostName是GIt平台域名，user一般使用系统用户git即可，IdentityFile则指定对应的私钥文件地址。</p><p>测试一下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line">kex_exchange_identification: Connection closed by remote host</span><br><span class="line">Connection closed by 192.30.255.113 port 22</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>显示Git远程连接关闭，上网查了一下类似问题，可能是电脑设置的梯子封禁了 Github 端口 22 的连接，将 Github 的连接端口从 22 改为 443 即可。继续修改config，将HostName改成ssh.githu.com，Port改为443。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Host accountB.github</span><br><span class="line">    HostName ssh.github.com</span><br><span class="line">    user git</span><br><span class="line">    Port 443</span><br><span class="line">    IdentityFile &quot;~/.ssh/id_rsa&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    IdentitiesOnly yes</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Host accountC.github</span><br><span class="line">    HostName ssh.github.com</span><br><span class="line">    user git</span><br><span class="line">    Port 443</span><br><span class="line">    IdentityFile &quot;~/.ssh/id_rsa_accountC&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    IdentitiesOnly yes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>测试一下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ssh -T git@accountC.github</span><br><span class="line">The authenticity of host &#x27;[ssh.github.com]:443 ([192.30.255.122]:443)&#x27; can&#x27;t be established.</span><br><span class="line">ED25219 key fingerprint is SHA256:+DiY3wxxV6TuJJhbpZisF/zLDA0zPMSvHdkr4UvCOqU.</span><br><span class="line">This key is not known by any other names</span><br><span class="line">Are you sure you want to continue connecting (yes/no/[fingerprint])? yes</span><br><span class="line">Warning: Permanently added &#x27;[ssh.github.com]:443&#x27; (ED25219) to the list of known hosts.</span><br><span class="line">Hi accountC! You&#x27;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>建立ssh连接成功。相应的也可以再执行一下ssh -T <a href="mailto:&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#x40;&#97;&#99;&#x63;&#111;&#x75;&#110;&#x74;&#66;&#46;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#x62;">&#x67;&#105;&#x74;&#x40;&#97;&#99;&#x63;&#111;&#x75;&#110;&#x74;&#66;&#46;&#x67;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#x62;</a>。</p><p>4.重新回到项目中，修改远程仓库的连接。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote set-url origin git@accountC.github/accountC/someproject.git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再执行一下提交，提交成功！</p><p>参考链接：</p><p><a href="https://idreamshen.github.io/posts/github-connection-closed/">Github Clone: Connection closed by remote host</a></p><p><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1952800">同机多Github账号配置多个SSH</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> SSH,Git </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>如何为Git创建SSH Key</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/23/How-to-create-SSH-key-for-Git/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/23/How-to-create-SSH-key-for-Git/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天尝试从BitBucket通过SSH下载项目，发现下载失败报如下错误：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git@bitbucket.org: Permission denied (publickey).</span><br><span class="line">fatal: Could not read from remote repository.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Please make sure you have the correct access rights</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>原来是本机没有设置SSH Keys给BitBucket，立即创建一个。</p><p>1.首先可以通过命令测试一下是否连接成功：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ssh -T git@bitbucket.org</span><br><span class="line">git@bitbucket.org: Permission denied (publickey). // 报错显示无权限</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.接下来创建密钥。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;youremailname@gmail.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>添加命令参数-f othername，可以自定义存放密钥的文件名，如：ssh-keygen -t rsa -C “<a href="mailto:&#121;&#x6f;&#x75;&#114;&#101;&#x6d;&#x61;&#105;&#x6c;&#x40;&#x67;&#x6d;&#97;&#x69;&#x6c;&#x2e;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;">&#121;&#x6f;&#x75;&#114;&#101;&#x6d;&#x61;&#105;&#x6c;&#x40;&#x67;&#x6d;&#97;&#x69;&#x6c;&#x2e;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;</a>“ -f 。</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>可以通过-h查看更多命令参数的使用，如：ssh-keygen -h。</p></blockquote><p>默认情况下，命令会在&#x2F;Users&#x2F;yourusername&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;目录下创建id_rsa和id_rsa.pub两个文件。id_rsa存的是私钥，id_rsa.pub存的是公钥。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(base) yourname@Mac BitBucket % ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;youremailname@gmail.com&quot;</span><br><span class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file in which to save the key (/Users/yourname/.ssh/id_rsa):</span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase):</span><br><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:</span><br><span class="line">Your identification has been saved in /Users/yourname/.ssh/id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved in /Users/yourname/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class="line">SHA256:hpGRCvxfRqPcHUhhuCWzcVkQI3YuV821QzL7B7/e0aE youremailname@gmail.com</span><br><span class="line">The key&#x27;s randomart image is:</span><br><span class="line">+---[RSA 3072]----+</span><br><span class="line">| .    ++OBooo.o  |</span><br><span class="line">|  o  .*BBo. o= . |</span><br><span class="line">|   o o+%oo .. +  |</span><br><span class="line">|    o ==+ .  . + |</span><br><span class="line">|     ..oS     ..o|</span><br><span class="line">|      ..      ..+|</span><br><span class="line">|             E o.|</span><br><span class="line">|              . o|</span><br><span class="line">|               ..|</span><br><span class="line">+----[SHA256]-----+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来将id_rsa.pub文件中的公钥内容拷贝到BitBucket，<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/bitbucket.png" alt="Bitbucket 操作界面"><br>最后用命令测试一下是否连接成功。出现以下提示表示连接成功。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ssh -T git@bitbucket.org</span><br><span class="line">authenticated via ssh key.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">You can use git to connect to Bitbucket. Shell access is disabled</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来就可以从BitBucket通过SSH下载项目了。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> SSH,Git </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>如何使用ExpressVPN代理上网</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/21/How-to-use-expressvpn/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/21/How-to-use-expressvpn/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>ExpressVPN是众多传统vpn服务商中比较知名的一个品牌。他家产品翻墙速度快，面对新的防火墙策略也能比较快应对。购买15个月的话平均每个月不到7美元，价格也比较合适。同时支持5台设备，可以多人均摊就更划算了。一个月内不满意还可以全额退款，这里就试试它了。</p><h1 id="购买ExpressVPN服务"><a href="#购买ExpressVPN服务" class="headerlink" title="购买ExpressVPN服务"></a>购买ExpressVPN服务</h1><p>首先访问官网，<a href="https://www.expressvpn.com/">https://www.expressvpn.com/</a> ，选择合适的套餐进行购买。这里选择了12个月的套餐。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn1.png" alt="Get ExpressVPN"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn2.png" alt="ExpressVPN plans price"></p><p>输入邮箱和支付信息，点“Join Now”就买好了。<br><img src="https://cœn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn3.png" alt="Input Email and Payment"></p><p>等待系统处理。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn4.png" alt="Processing payment"></p><p>修改账户密码。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn5.png" alt="Change ExpressVPN password"></p><p>系统会跳到到设置页面，页面上的激活码很重要，用于激活应用。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn6.png" alt="Activation Code"></p><h1 id="安装电脑端"><a href="#安装电脑端" class="headerlink" title="安装电脑端"></a>安装电脑端</h1><p>下面以Mac电脑为例进行应用安装。选择Mac，点击Download，下载对应的PKG文件。下载后双击文件安装。<br>打开ExpressVPN应用，根据界面提示输入激活码，一路点击确定或继续，最终进入到主页面。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn7.png" alt="Connecting on Mac"></p><p>多等一会时间，等待连接完成。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn8.png" alt="Connected on Mac"></p><h1 id="安装手机端"><a href="#安装手机端" class="headerlink" title="安装手机端"></a>安装手机端</h1><p>如果是手机端需要连接VPN，则需要下手机端的APP。<br>以Iphone为例，ExpressVPN在大陆区搜不到，需要将App Store账号切换成如美区AppleID进行下载。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn9.png" alt="Download ExpressVPN on IOS"></p><p>下载后打开APP，点击Sign in进行账号登陆。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn10.png" alt="Sign in"></p><p>看过条款内容后，点按钮同意条款。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn11.png" alt="Agree and continue"></p><p>接下来ExpressVPN会添加手机的VPN设置，点击“允许”进行授权。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn12.png" alt="Grant for VPN config"></p><p>输入手机密码，完成授权。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn13.png" alt="Press in iphone password"></p><p>应用询问允不允许它发通知给用户。OK则同意，否则不同意，请按需选择。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn14.png" alt="Grant for notification"></p><p>如果选择同意，应用会调起系统通知提示，按需选择。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn15.png" alt="Agree for notification"></p><p>应用询问是否愿意分享使用数据，帮助提升应用。这里也是按心意选择，怕麻烦就“No thanks”了。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn16.png" alt="Ask if help improve expressVPN"></p><p>设置完成后进入主界面，可以看到中间有个开关图标的按钮。Not connected则是没链接，点击按钮尝试连接。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn17.png" alt="home page showing not connected"></p><p>显示Connected，则表示连接成功。一开始连接可能会花较长时间，请耐心等待一会。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn18.png" alt="VPN connected"></p><p>如果想了解ExpressVPN做了哪些VPN设置。可以打开手机的“设置”&#x3D;&gt;“VPN”进行查看，VPN状态是打开的，连接的是ExpressVPN Lightway。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn19.png" alt="Check Iphone VPN config"></p><p>接下来验证一下是否能翻墙。比如下载Youtube，看看视频能不能正常播发。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn20.png" alt="Check whether the VPN works"></p><p>打开APP，视频能正常播放。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn21.png" alt="Youtube works successfully"></p><p>翻墙成功，可以科学上网了！</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> expressVPN </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>如何通过Iphone拔卡访问TikTok</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/21/How-to-use-tiktok/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/21/How-to-use-tiktok/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>TikTok在大陆地区无法直接下载使用，需要进行一些特殊操作。折腾调研了一番，发现还是拔卡方案最简单有效。这里记录一下通过Iphone拔卡使用TikTok的方法。</p><h1 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h1><ul><li>1部Iphone手机，建议系统版本在10.0及以上。</li><li>1个海外AppleID账号，美区台湾地区等都可以，一般首选美区。</li><li>1个邮箱或海外手机号，用于注册TikTok账号，建议使用国外邮箱如Outlook邮箱邮箱，一般首选Gmail邮箱。</li><li>可以访问外网的VPN环境。</li></ul><h1 id="调整手机环境"><a href="#调整手机环境" class="headerlink" title="调整手机环境"></a>调整手机环境</h1><p>接下来对IPhone进行一些设置，绕开TikTok对国内环境的检查和访问限制，让TikTok判定不是国内环境从而正常运行。所以这时如果已经下载了TikTok，先不要打开它。</p><ul><li>拔掉IPhone的SIM卡。</li><li>打开IPhone的设置&#x3D;&gt;隐私，关掉定位服务。</li><li>打开IPhone的设置&#x3D;&gt;通用&#x3D;&gt;语言与地区，把地区设置为美国。</li><li>打开App Store，登陆准备好的美区AppleID，搜索TikTok应用。下载后先不打开它。</li><li>打开准备好的VPN环境。</li><li>打开TikTok应用。<br>有视频能正常播放就表示TikTok能访问了。</li></ul><blockquote><p>PC端可以访问：<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/">https://www.tiktok.com/</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Tiktok </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
