      <title>如何购买Shadowrocket</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/21/How-to-buy-shadowrocket/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/21/How-to-buy-shadowrocket/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Shadowrocket在大陆区App Store没有上架，可以在App Store登陆美区Apple ID购买。购买时需要绑定信用卡，如果没有有效信用卡或者不想绑定的话，可以走充值购买。下面记录一下如何通过充值购买付费APP。</p><p>1.访问充值平台如：<a href="https://ididhub.com/">https://ididhub.com/</a> 。购买一张29.99面值的充值卡，可以覆盖Shadowrocket的2.99美元售价。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok1.png" alt="iIdidhub home page"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok2.png" alt="Refill card details"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok3.png" alt="Confirm order"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok4.png" alt="Payment page"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok5.png" alt="Gift card password"></p><p>2.打开Iphone手机的App Store，点击右上角的图标进入账户页。点击“兑换充值卡或代码”，“手动输入兑换码”。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok6.png" alt="Exchange recharge card or code"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok7.png" alt="Enter the conversion code manually"></p><p>3.充值成功后便可以购买付费软件了。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/buy_shadowrocket/buy_shdrok8.png" alt="Buying paid apps"></p>]]></content>
      
      
