      <title>Markdown语法速记表</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/18/Markdown-cheat-sheet/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/18/Markdown-cheat-sheet/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>markdown有很多衍生版本。附带了额外的markdown命令。下面介绍基本的markdown语法。</p><span id="more"></span><h3 id="标题（Headers）"><a href="#标题（Headers）" class="headerlink" title="标题（Headers）"></a>标题（Headers）</h3><p>1到6级标题。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 标题 1</span><br><span class="line">## 标题 2</span><br><span class="line">### 标题 3</span><br><span class="line">#### 标题 4</span><br><span class="line">##### 标题 5</span><br><span class="line">###### 标题 6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="强调（Emphasis）"><a href="#强调（Emphasis）" class="headerlink" title="强调（Emphasis）"></a>强调（Emphasis）</h3><p>粗体，斜体，以及粗体和斜体结合。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**粗体**</span><br><span class="line">__粗体__</span><br><span class="line">*斜体*</span><br><span class="line">_斜体_</span><br><span class="line">_斜体**结合**粗体_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="列表（Lists）"><a href="#列表（Lists）" class="headerlink" title="列表（Lists）"></a>列表（Lists）</h3><p>无序列表和有序列表。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* 表项1</span><br><span class="line">* 表项2</span><br><span class="line">    * 表项2-1</span><br><span class="line">    * 表项2-2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 表项1</span><br><span class="line">2. 表项2</span><br><span class="line">    * 表项2-1</span><br><span class="line">    * 表项2-2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="图片（Images）"><a href="#图片（Images）" class="headerlink" title="图片（Images）"></a>图片（Images）</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![图片描述信息](http://image.url.com)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="链接（Links）"><a href="#链接（Links）" class="headerlink" title="链接（Links）"></a>链接（Links）</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[链接文字](http://link.url.com)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="引号（Blockquotes）"><a href="#引号（Blockquotes）" class="headerlink" title="引号（Blockquotes）"></a>引号（Blockquotes）</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; 书写引文文本。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="内联代码（Inline-code）"><a href="#内联代码（Inline-code）" class="headerlink" title="内联代码（Inline code）"></a>内联代码（Inline code）</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">普通文本`高亮文本`文本文本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 前端 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> markdown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
